{"tid":657384,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"大家小心d輪椅黨 尋晚差d比人打荷包","createTime":"2018-05-08T05:11:53.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-08T07:42:50.000Z","uid":98507,"like":61,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"287fadd06191a8432349b7e35e0ac9a9ae793139","tid":657384,"uid":98507,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-08T05:11:53.000Z","msg":"話說尋晚係商場行行下<br />\n有個坐住輪椅嘅人同我講<br />\n「靚仔做個好心 推我去巴士站好唔好呀？唔該你丫靚仔」<br />\n我見佢咁撚誠實 咪幫幫佢<br />\n點知行行下有兩條木嘴好似左右護法咁痴埋黎我身後面<br />\n我擰轉頭望一望又行遠少少 轉個頭又行返近<br />\n屌佢老母當我係狐狸先生呀？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n重覆左三四之後<br />\n個輪椅撚同我講<br />\n「我到呢度得喇唔該」<br />\n但佢個樣好明顯係黑過閪<br />\n行兩步回一回頭見佢原路折返<br />\n我好奇跟一跟蹤<br />\n竟然見到又搵第二個幫佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過冇人so佢<br />\n到呢度我先知呢班陷家剷係仆街仔黎<br />\n嬲到我即刻搵保安趕佢地走<br />\n大家小心呢d撚頭 真係好心著雷劈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nbtw好彩佢冇係個手柄搽aa膠<br />\n如果唔係到時佢偷完野棄車逃走<br />\n我就推住架輪椅on99"},{"pid":"71f40eecff3c5f99480a8ab6f23039352b67dee5","tid":657384,"uid":5760,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-08T05:13:38.000Z","msg":"aa 膠 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0023b502c32a6d8d7101c1a7385ea0b433e5c379","tid":657384,"uid":33864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-08T05:15:50.000Z","msg":"心地好就畀佢呃<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 人渣"},{"pid":"b971a7c81c20b84b62931bce83ae5a48c296c75e","tid":657384,"uid":40588,"like":0,"dislike":24,"score":-24,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-08T05:21:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/08/132105_16d2763a575b9dc3212284b86e2d2e29.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https